PayPal Mobile Express Checkout
==============================

This is a MonoTouch binding for PayPal's Mobile Express Checkout Library which
can be found at

    https://www.x.com/sites/default/files/PayPal_MECL_1.0.3_iPhone-Developer-Package.zip


Building
========

To build the bindings, run the `make` command from within the bindings
directory.

To build the sample project, open PayPalSample.sln in MonoDevelop and run it.


Using PayPal.dll with your own iOS App
======================================

Simply add PayPal.dll to your project's References in MonoDevelop and you are
good to go!
